ympics\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I have worked so hard for nothing.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I gave everything for two years and today it did not work.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is nothing positive today.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think these were my last Games and I did not succeed in enjoying them.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Games\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not have fun.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am happy to see the crowd there for us, it warms my heart.\\\"\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starting on uneven bars, de Jesus dos Santos fell early in her routine and while she recovered to hit the dismount, the early misstep was just the beginning.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999197458651143, \"rank\": 8.020147872878426e-05, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"uneven bars\", \"from